Sentencas: La0.4Sr0.6Co0.7Fe0.2Nb0.1O3-delta-Gd0.2Ce0.8O2-delta (LSCFN-GDC) with high catalytic performance was synthesized by one-step co-synthesis method for developing a symmetrical reversible solid oxide cell (SOC) electrode.
Titulo: La0.4Sr0.6Co0.7Fe0.2Nb0.1O3-δ-Gd0.2Ce0.8O2-δ as Symmetrical Electrode Material for Reversible Solid Oxide Cells

Sentencas: Electrolyte-supported symmetrical SOCs were fabricated by tape-casting and screen-printing methods with La0.8Sr0.2Ga0.83Mg0.17O3-delta (LSGM) as the electrolyte and LSCFN-GDC as both anode and cathode.
Titulo: La0.4Sr0.6Co0.7Fe0.2Nb0.1O3-δ-Gd0.2Ce0.8O2-δ as Symmetrical Electrode Material for Reversible Solid Oxide Cells

Sentencas: The configuration of SOC is LSCFN-GDC parallel to LSGM parallel to LSCFN-GDC.
Titulo: La0.4Sr0.6Co0.7Fe0.2Nb0.1O3-δ-Gd0.2Ce0.8O2-δ as Symmetrical Electrode Material for Reversible Solid Oxide Cells

Sentencas: Solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) and solid oxide electrolysis cell (SOEC) modes were used to test the performance of SOCs.
Titulo: La0.4Sr0.6Co0.7Fe0.2Nb0.1O3-δ-Gd0.2Ce0.8O2-δ as Symmetrical Electrode Material for Reversible Solid Oxide Cells

Sentencas: The results show that the maximum power densities are 1.036, 0.996, 0.479, and 0.952 W/cm(2) under the atmosphere of fuel gas of H-2 (3% H2O),
Titulo: La0.4Sr0.6Co0.7Fe0.2Nb0.1O3-δ-Gd0.2Ce0.8O2-δ as Symmetrical Electrode Material for Reversible Solid Oxide Cells

Sentencas: H-2 (0.01% H2S), CH4, and C3H8 at 850 degrees C, respectively.
Titulo: La0.4Sr0.6Co0.7Fe0.2Nb0.1O3-δ-Gd0.2Ce0.8O2-δ as Symmetrical Electrode Material for Reversible Solid Oxide Cells

Sentencas: The current density at the electrolytic voltage of 1.3 V is 0.943 A/cm(2) during the electrolysis of H-2 (50% H2O).
Titulo: La0.4Sr0.6Co0.7Fe0.2Nb0.1O3-δ-Gd0.2Ce0.8O2-δ as Symmetrical Electrode Material for Reversible Solid Oxide Cells

Sentencas: LSCFN-GDC has good coking-resistance, sulfur-tolerance, and redox stability, and its stable performance can be sustained for 700 h under the atmosphere of H-2 (0.01% H2S), CH4, H-2 (3% H2O), and H-2 (50% H2O).
Titulo: La0.4Sr0.6Co0.7Fe0.2Nb0.1O3-δ-Gd0.2Ce0.8O2-δ as Symmetrical Electrode Material for Reversible Solid Oxide Cells

Sentencas: The results indicate that the one-step method is a facile and optimized fabrication procedure of electrode and LSCFN-GDC parallel to LSGM parallel to LSCFN-GDC SOCs have great potential in further application.
Titulo: La0.4Sr0.6Co0.7Fe0.2Nb0.1O3-δ-Gd0.2Ce0.8O2-δ as Symmetrical Electrode Material for Reversible Solid Oxide Cells
